</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://www-personal.umich.edu/~lormand/phil/cons/qualia.htm" class="external text" title="http://www-personal.umich.edu/~lormand/phil/cons/qualia.htm" rel="nofollow"><i>Qualia!</i> (Now Showing at a Theatre Near You)</a> — By Eric Lormand. A response to Dennett.</li>
