<li><a href="http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/qualia-knowledge/" class="external text" title="http://plato.stanford.edu/entries/qualia-knowledge/" rel="nofollow">Qualia: The Knowledge Argument</a> — by Martine Nida-Rümelin.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://www.imprint.co.uk/rama/qualia.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.imprint.co.uk/rama/qualia.pdf" rel="nofollow">Three Laws of Qualia</a> — by <a href="/wiki/Vilayanur_S._Ramachandran" title="Vilayanur S. Ramachandran">Ramachandran</a> and <a href="/wiki/William_Hirstein" title="William Hirstein">Hirstein</a> (biological perspective).</li>
</ul>
